00:30:01.728 --> 00:30:05.268
So I think there's another interesting story, but I need to do some further

509
00:30:05.308 --> 00:30:09.208
analysis onto which cell types I want to include in the niche. Does that help?

510
00:30:09.488 --> 00:30:13.028
Yep. So they're in the tumor, but close to the TLS or in some

511
00:30:13.068 --> 00:30:13.628
